title: COVID-19 in Canada
description: Total of 1,507,092 confirmed cases and 26,989 deaths are reported, with over 65% of the population fully vaccinated in Canada on 31 Aug 2021. Is vaccination effectively preventing the spread of virus reamins questionable. Data from Our World in Data, retrieved on 1 Sep 2021.

title: Current COVID-19 and Vaccination Status in Chile
description: As on 31 August 2021, 1,638,675 confirmed cases and 36,937 deaths have been recorded, however, the good news is over 70% of the population in Chile is now fully vaccinated. Data from Our World in Data, retrieved on 1 Sep 2021.

title: Data Description
description: The dataset used in this blog is retrieved from Our World in Data on 1 Sep 2021.
contents:
The dataset used for tables, plots and analysis is retrieved from Our World in Data on 1 September 2021, with all data up to date from 23 February 2020 to 31 August 2021. This dataset is publicly available and completely open access under the Creative Commons BY license (Ritchie et al., 2020), and is allowed to be used for analysis purpose of this blog.
Data Cleaning
The original dataset includes data from 233 countries, contains 62 columns and 113313 observations. This blog only focus on the COVID-19 situation in selected countries, and the areas of interests are only related to confirmed cases, number of tests conducted, number of death and vaccinations performed.
Therefore, the dataset has been filtered and selected with only records associated with selected countries and relevant variables, stored in a tidy format for analysis purpose of this report.
The filtered dataset contains 17 variables and 556 observations from Feb 2020 to Aug 2021, the description of the variables included are listed in the following section.

title: Welcome to A Study of Global COVID-19 Situation
description: Welcome to A Study of Global COVID-19 Situation, we hope you enjoy the tables, plots and posts here!
contents:
A Study of Global COVID-19 Situation aims to provide tables, plots and related analysis regarding the COVID-19 situation and vaccination status in multiple countries around the world.
Tables, plots and data description can be found in posts and/or related sections on navigation bar.
Dataset used for creating the tables, plots and posts was retrieved from Our World in Data on 1 September 2021, data contained is updated from February 2020 to 31 August 2021.
Detailed data description and source citation can be found in Data Description.
